item.description:
In this scenario, we create

1 Project

2 Types + 1 Parking Lot

5 + 5 + 2 Itemz

"Type 1" 5 itemz as Parent trace to "Type 2" 5 Itemz

"Type 1" 1st and 5th itemz as Parent trace to "Parking Lot" 2 Itemz

"Type 2" 1st and 5th itemz as Parent trace to "Parking Lot" 2 Itemz

In Total we create 9 traces.
